I am having negitive thoughts about my self. and I am realizing why its so hard for me to have a realation ship with some one. and it comes down to I'm scared. cause I am fucked up in the head and have had many bad realationships. there are few people I trust in this world. are the ones I do I cherish and never want to loose. so dont ever leave ok?

Hello... I am sitting here... And I dont have a clue what I am going to say. Things are fucked up in my house right now. Its not a huge house. And yet I hardly see my brother. He's like a ghost. And I havent talked to him in two days. Except to say. "give me my phone". Its strange. I feel strange. Everything is strang. When I was running down that road at 12 nothing felt real. It was strange. I guess I will just talk about what I did today. I went to my moms friends house. Teri and Joe. Their really cool people. Joe tought me a song on guitar a while ago and I played it. Except I found a better way of playing it. It was just fun. It was a long drive out there. And my mom stoped at the one gift store place for like half an hour! or longer. It started to get on my nerves. But it was allright I guess. I got to get out of the house with my mom. I am going to go... maybe go to bed. I dont know. goodnight world if anyone is out there steveo out
